[*]AutoPickup: Skip full-ammo bullet boxes to avoid rapid failed pickup loops
[*]ConfigUI: Description bar now auto-resizes height with text wrapping for long descriptions
[*]QuickSceneSwitch: Added warning about cutscene/story event usage
[/list]

